Class SimpleEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.IDObject
      • graph.SimpleEdge
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Flowable, Weighted, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class SimpleEdge
extends IDObject
implements Flowable, Weighted, java.lang.Cloneable
    A simple edge implementation for use in SimpleGraph. Implements the Flowable and Weighted interfaces to that the SimpleGraph is appropriate for use in shortest path or max flow algorithms.
    Author:
    Mshnik
